item.title: Error Connecting to server
item.dc:creator: @moparisthebest Moparisthebest
item.description:
@moparisthebest wrote:

[quote=“zacharymata, post:1, topic:416”][glow=red,2,300]Does this mean that it has been updated? I have Aryan 363. I am using a proxy. If it is that I have my proxy messed up. Please point it out. this is my code.[/glow] @echo off title Running Bot java -DsocksProxyHost=67.188.112.11:2301 -DsocksProxyPort=58 -noverify -Xmx500m -cp .;./OUTPUT;./OUTPUT/unrenamed.jar;./BotClasses; Bot pause[/quote]

change that to:

@echo off title Running Bot java -DsocksProxyHost=67.188.112.11 -DsocksProxyPort=2301 -noverify -Xmx500m -cp .;./OUTPUT;./OUTPUT/unrenamed.jar;./BotClasses; Bot pause

you put the ip as the host, and the port as the port, no colons
